Julie McWhirter https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Julie_McWhirter 0 Julie McWhirter (born October 12, 1947), also known as Julie Dees and Julie McWhirter-Dees, is a retired American voice actress and impressionist best known for her work as Jeannie in the animated version of Jeannie, Bubbles in Jabberjaw and Baby Smurf and Sassette in The Smurfs.
